body:
Ms. Jefferson,

In order to address your question, would you please provide the following information in a written format:

1)  Your complete name, address and telephone number;

2)  The date, time and location of your contact with the officer;

3)  The name of the officer, if you have that information;

4)  The name(s) of any witness(es);

5)  A detailed written description of your encounter;

6) And lastly, any other information that would aid in the review.

Thank you for your inquiring and I await your response.

Cordially,

Chief J. Jett
Alpena Police Department
Alpena, Michigan
